ActPilotage Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of BERNARD MORENCY of Saint-Lambert, Quebec, to be a member of the Laurentian Pilotage Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years; and approves his appointment to be part-time Vice-Chairperson of the Laurentian Pilotage Authority.
